snippet.title: Sonic: Fan Games/Hacks 519: Sonic Shift (SAGE2006)
snippet.description:
(These are my simple game play videos)
(I can and will remove specific videos if its necessary/requested)

Name: Sonic Shift - SAGE2006
Credit: ?
Release Date: August 24th, 2006

My Website: https://scaleyfoxy.weebly.com/

Download: Only on Site.

00:00 - Menu
00:27 - Northern Woodlands Act 1
04:22 - Northern Woodlands Act 2
06:41 - Boss
08:41 - Azure Lake Zone Test Act
10:46 - Sky Deck

NOTES: AND we are back in 2D Sonic.
In good old SAGE2006 that barely has any info about it what so ever!
But here is a fangame from said timeline made by... Uh...
So anyway, here we have unique title that stands out for it's visuals.
The midis are also new to me, even some unfinished stages with unused music.
Could not really show those off but one of em was labeled Echidna Empire hmm...
Meanwhile another key feature here is Tikal being playable and she has special move...
Very interesting indeed, overall I don't have too much info about this title.
But it's overall pretty interesting tho the window resolution is comedically tiny.
